videos.description: Joseph Girard III finds Quincy Guerrier cutting backdoor for the alley-oop dunk, plus the foul.

videos.description: Marek Dolezaj drives and gets crafty for the layup to cut into Florida State's lead.

videos.description: RaiQuan Gray grabs the rebound and throws the ball ahead to Balsa Koprivica for the two-handed slam.
